This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. Composes swift-gzip (RFC 1952) and swift-zlib (RFC 1950)
behind a single header-driven `decode(_:contentEncoding:)` entry point
matching the HTTP `Content-Encoding` header semantics from RFC 9110
§ 8.4 and RFC 7230 § 4.2.2.

RFC 9110: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc9110.html
RFC 7230: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc7230.html
